description: Enforces PEP 8, Ruff formatting, and strict line limits.
globs: 
alwaysApply: false
---
- **Strict PEP 8/Ruff**: Adhere strictly to PEP 8. Assume code will be processed by uff format and uff check --fix.
- **Line Length**: Max 79 characters per line. Break lines logically.
- **Imports**: Use absolute imports. Group stdlib, third-party, local. isort compatible. NEVER modify existing imports unless fixing a lint error or explicitly asked.
- **Whitespace**: Use standard PEP 8 whitespace rules (e.g., around operators, after commas).
